{
  "stem": "3097.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The pogrom happened July 4, 1946.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I was in the security working, I used to frequent the Planty 7 where about 200 Jews used to stay there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, on the river.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The river, Silnica, was a river bisecting our city in-- in-- in two parts.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I used to, some way, give them the security to some extent, you see, help them out, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of the people had guns there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when I left it was-- I left about, what, seven months before the pogrom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The pogrom started that way-- a child supposedly was lost someplace, a boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't find him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Finally, he did come out to the surface, and he said that some people took him in a basement of a building.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they beat him up and did something to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the parents, before, started to look for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went to the-- to the security.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody could find him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What actually happened, he went to a village by himself and was afraid to tell the parents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the woman, the mother, the woman started to say and yell out that the Jews who are on Planty 7 tried to kill-- and they killed probably some other Polish Christian children-- to get the blood for the matzah OK?",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or to drink the blood because they came from the concentration camps, and they need to-- to be healthy, or something to-- to make them seem little more stronger.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they primitive people and some other people who wanted to do that because it was still a revolution at that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The regime, which came from Russia and took over the-- the government in Poland, was anti-capitalistic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was under Stalin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
